neSecondaryStandBy.name: neSecondaryStandBy
neSecondaryStandBy.description: This trap is sent when the secondary NE changes to StandBy mode

neSecondaryBypass.name: neSecondaryBypass
neSecondaryBypass.description: This trap is sent when the secondary NE changes to Bypass mode

collTableOverFlow.name: collTableOverFlow
collTableOverFlow.description: This trap is sent when acounting is not reading from the collector which causes the collector table to exceeds limits
